title: Shingeki no Kyojin - Not a Love Song (Doujinshi)
description:
Pairing: Levi x Eren

Not a Love Song:
Story about trust between Captain Levi and Eren.

Egoist:
Eren returns to normal after being retrained, but loses all memory of what happened when he was in confinement, so does this story get a happy ending in the end?
